<br>
Doubtlessly you can increase your damage output by purchasing +int and +mana items, but the only serious item that can be considered is Solist's Icy Wand.   Only the truly rich and fortunate nead apply, however, this wand is not only powerful, but extremely rare.<br>
<br>
The beauty of SIW is that it is a right clickable item that does 38 Direct Damage every six seconds, and must be used from the Primary or Secondary Melee slot.  It has no stat bonuses.<br>
<br>
It is found off of random skeleton and burynai monsters in Kurns Tower, in the middle of the Field of Bone.<br>
<br>
It is among the rarest drops in the game, more rare perhaps than the Glowing Black Stone.  Wizards have spent days at a time AOEing the entire floor in a single cast without ever getting one.  Rumors of newbies looting one and selling them to vendors for 6 plat have been heard and mourned.<br>
<br>
It first works at level 12, where it is a godly addition to a wizards arsenal, and makes a competent down time reducer well into the low 40's.<br>
